<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>All hail King Jesus</title>
<aka>Kom hyll Kong Jesus!</aka>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Kom hyll Kong Jesus!
 Kom hyll Immanuel!
 Lys og liv, håp og kraft,
 Du har all makt.
 For hver dag, Du gir meg liv,
 vil jeg Deg prise,
 i all evighet får jeg bo hos Deg.

[V2]
 All hail King Jesus,
 All hail Emmanuel.
 King of Kings, Lord of Lords,
 Bright morning star.
 And throughout eternity
 I'm going to praise Him
 And forevermore,
 I will reign with Him.</lyrics>
<key>D</key>
<presentation>v1 v2 </presentation>
</song>